Ext.data.JsonP['Alloy_5.4.0.GA_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Alloy 5.4.0.GA - 10 August 2016</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46255258\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Alloy 5.4.0.GA - 10 August 2016</h1>\n    <p>Alloy 5.4.0.GA is a minor release that includes new features, improvements and bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46255258_Alloy5.4.0.GAReleaseNote-NewFeatures\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>New Features</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1481\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1481</a> - Data binding: Support binding multiple models to the same view    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p class=\"p1\">Support binding multiple models to the same view    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1482\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1482</a> - Data binding: Support deep binding of model object attributes    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p class=\"p1\">Support deep binding of model attributes    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1494\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1494</a> - iOS: Support Ti.UI.iOS.Stepper in Alloy    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p class=\"p1\">Added support for the new Stepper UI element on iOS    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46255258_Alloy5.4.0.GAReleaseNote-Improvements\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Improvements</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1281\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1281</a> - RSS sample should be removed in favour of Studio version    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Updated the RSS sample to reflect recent changes to Studio    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46255258_Alloy5.4.0.GAReleaseNote-FixedIssues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issues</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1478\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1478</a> - Data binding fails when binding string or model attribute name has dash, space or quote    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1480\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1480</a> - Bug/Regression: Data binding always returns string values    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1486\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1486</a> - iOS, Android: Global styles is not overridden by local styles for orientationModes.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1503\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1503</a> - After Alloy compile, property which has array disappear.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1508\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1508</a> - iOS: Localised splash screen is not visible    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46255258\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Alloy 5.4.0.GA Release Note"});